analysis_result.summary: The rental agreement pertains to the property located at Flat No. 302, Rose Residency, Baner, Pune - 411045, India. The owner of the property is Mr. Rajesh Sharma, whose permanent address is 23, Green Park Society, Pune. The tenant, Ms. Priya Nair, is a software engineer at Infosys Pune with her permanent address in Kochi, Kerala. The monthly rent is set at INR 25,000, and a maintenance charge of INR 2,000 is also applicable. A security deposit of INR 75,000 was paid, as evidenced by Cheque No. 128756 dated 01/03/2022.
